  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  AddContextToTheGameObject: "This is a demo for showing off the player movement
    script. \nOpen up the script to see more details\nThere are 3 different movement
    types that change how the player moves\n\nAcceleration will affect how fast you
    move\nMax speed will clamp the velocity\nRotation speed only applies to the Relative
    Force movement\n\nLock Y Input will make only left and write input affect the
    player\nEnable jump will allow you to jump with space bar\nJump force changes
    how much you jump\n\nTry navigating the level using the different movement types
    with different values to see how they work\n"
